  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Warehouse Assistant (Forklift License)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Duties:</strong></p><ul><li>Receive, inspect, and store incoming goods in the warehouse.</li><li>Picking and packing of goods according to the packing list and delivery order.</li><li>Load and unload trucks using equipment such as forklifts, pallet jacks, and hand trucks.</li><li>Perform inventory counts and maintain accurate records.</li><li>Inspect products for any defects or damage before packaging to maintain quality standards.</li><li>Communicate any issues or discrepancies with orders to supervisors.</li><li>Support e-commerce operations by picking and packing online orders accurately and efficiently.</li><li>Ensure warehouse is clean, organized, and safe at all times.</li><li>Perform any other duties assigned by the superior based on warehouse needs.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess a <strong>valid forklift license </strong></li><li>Comfortable working at elevated heights when required, with adherence to safety procedures and proper use of safety equipment</li><li>Basic literacy and numeracy skills to complete inventory records and documentation</li><li>Ability to work independently as well as in a team environment</li><li>Willingness to perform shift work, overtime, or weekend work if operationally required</li><li>Prior warehouse or logistics experience is an advantage but not mandatory</li></ul><p>Working Hours: 7AM - 4PM, 7AM - 11AM (5.5days, rest day on Sunday)<br /><br />Liz Ooi Li Chen (R1104561)<br />Recruit Express Services Pte Ltd (13C6614)</p>",
